dsDescriptionValue.value: The datasets presented here are: (1) Mitochondrial Genome-Encoded Proteins Identified by Tandem Mass Spectrometry (MS/MS) of Purified Acanthamoeba castellanii Mitochondria. (2) Nuclear-Genome Encoded Proteins Identified by Tandem Mass Spectrometry (MS/MS) in Purified Acanthamoeba castellanii Mitochondria. (3) Putative Nuclear Genome-Encoded, Contaminant Proteins Identified by Tandem Mass Spectrometry (MS/MS) of Purified Acanthamoeba castellanii Mitochondria. (4) Acanthamoeba castellani Mitochondrial Proteins Identified in silico
